name: Pebble Watchface - TJ Schedule
tagline: A Pebble Watchface designed to display the daily schedule for TJHSST
body:
**Download the latest public app!**
**If you have an OG Pebble, Pebble Steel, or even a Pebble Time, the app is compatible with your device!**
**https://apps.getpebble.com/applications/5611bb419af9900b3900004c**

### Convenient
Easily displays the TJHSST Schedule to the user, alongside pertinent information such as the time and the weather (future).

### Open Source
Fork me on Github!

### Authors and Contributors
Fully developed by @mk2018, but feel free to fork me!
